\contentsline {section}{\numberline {1}``条件概率" : $ P(A|\text {条件}B)=\genfrac {}{}{}0{P(A\cap B)}{P(\text {条件}B)}=\genfrac {}{}{}0{\text {事件}A,B\text {同时发生的概率}}{\text {事件}B\text {发生的概率}} $}{2}{section.1}%
\contentsline {section}{\numberline {2}条件概率的性质}{4}{section.2}%
\contentsline {subsection}{\numberline {2.1}性质: $ P(A | \text {条件}B) >= 0$}{4}{subsection.2.1}%
\contentsline {subsection}{\numberline {2.2}性质: $ P(\Omega | \text {条件}B) = 1$}{4}{subsection.2.2}%
\contentsline {subsection}{\numberline {2.3}性质: $ \text {P}\left ( \text {A}_1\cup \text {A}_2\ |\text {B} \right ) =\text {P}\left ( \text {A}_1\ |\text {B} \right ) +\text {P}\left ( \text {A}_2\ |\text {B} \right ) -\text {P}\left ( \text {A}_1\text {A}_2\ |\text {B} \right ) $}{4}{subsection.2.3}%
\contentsline {subsection}{\numberline {2.4}性质: $ \text {P}\left ( \text {A\ |B} \right ) =1-\text {P}\left ( \overline {\text {A}}\ |\text {B} \right ) $}{4}{subsection.2.4}%
\contentsline {subsection}{\numberline {2.5}性质: 可列可加性: 若$ A_1, A_2, ... A_n, ...$ 是``互不相容"的事件, 则有: $ P(\DOTSB \sum@ \slimits@ _{i=1}^\infty A_i | B) = \DOTSB \sum@ \slimits@ _{i=1}^ \infty P(A_i | B)$ ← 即: ``和的概率", 等于``概率的和"}{4}{subsection.2.5}%
\contentsline {section}{\numberline {3}``条件概率"的乘法公式 : $ P(\text {前后})=P(\text {后}) \cdot P(\text {前}|\text {\text {后}}) = P(\text {\text {前}}) \cdot P(\text {后}|\text {前})$}{4}{section.3}%
